T9 algorithm implementation.

T9 algorithm demo http://t9.nerevar.com/

=============================================================================

Russian words vocabulary.
Source file size: 1,91 Mb == 1965,40 Kb == 2012571 b
Output file size: 4,06 Mb == 4162,59 Kb == 4262502 b
Total words: 161K

Scan whole file in RAM and iterate each line (each word) and recursively create Trie (prefix tree) with letter as an identifier of a tree node took 239.291070938 seconds using AMD Athlon 64 X2 Dual Core Processor 6000+ (2 CPUs), ~3.1GHz, Memory: 3072MB RAM, Windows 7 Pro x86, Open-server (http:/open-server.ru/)
Then recursively save tree to serialized file took 861.490472078 seconds 

